<p>Stacey, who is 11 years younger than Shane, has said they met when she in her early twenties.</p>

<p>'We met when I was very young, fell in love quickly and then tried to make it work for the kids,' she previously told Daily Mail Australia.</p>

<p>'It was a civil break-up. He's an amazing dad and I have no regrets.'  </p>

<p>Shane also has Stacey's name tattooed on his hand along with Kosta's name and birth date - January 25, 2016.</p>

