<p>Despite their endless arguments and cheating allegations on the show, the pair fuelled reconciliation rumours this month by meeting up on the Gold Coast.</p>

<p>However, during her recent Q&amp;A session on Instagram, she told fans they were 'just friends' and she was already 'committed to someone else'. </p>

